description: An Entertainer's Paradise! Lots of space! 2 BIG bedrooms (one up, one down), 2 full en suite baths condo w/ amazing exclusive private deck & private Zen garden. Bi-level, hardwood floors throughout, both bedrooms w/ ensuite bathrooms, large closets, 2 outdoor sheds, large dining room, jacuzzi tub, central air, plus bonus room off bedroom, great for a library/study, washer & dryer in the unit. 2 levels of living w/ 2 separate entrances. Brand NEW Heat/AC Unit. Very quiet street, yet very near Broadway.This one will not last.
